M|awesome-design-reference|Reference directory of 59 prd-grade design systems. Fetch any design system's full DESIGN.md from `https://getdesign.md/{site}/design-md`.
M|awesome-design-reference|These 12 design systems most closely match YVON's aesthetic — dark navy `#1A1A2E`, accent red `#E94560`, data-dense dashboard, dark cyberpunk professional.
M|awesome-design-reference|| Priority | Design System | Fetch URL | Why It Matches YVON |
M|awesome-design-reference||----------|--------------|-----------|---------------------|
M|awesome-design-reference|| 1 | Linear | `https://getdesign.md/linear.app/design-md` | Ultra-minimal dark, precise spacing, purple accent — closest vibe |
M|awesome-design-reference|| 2 | Vercel | `https://getdesign.md/vercel.com/design-md` | Black precision, card-based layouts, developer tool aesthetic |
M|awesome-design-reference|| 3 | Cursor | `https://getdesign.md/cursor.com/design-md` | Dark IDE-like interface, gradient accents — same domain (AI tool) |
M|awesome-design-reference|| 4 | Sentry | `https://getdesign.md/sentry.io/design-md` | Dark dashboard, data-dense, anl panels — exact YVON use case |
M|awesome-design-reference|| 5 | PostHog | `https://getdesign.md/posthog.com/design-md` | Developer-friendly anl dashboard, dark charts |
M|awesome-design-reference|| 6 | Supabase | `https://getdesign.md/supabase.com/design-md` | Dark emerald theme, code-first, green accent |
M|awesome-design-reference|| 7 | Stripe | `https://getdesign.md/stripe.com/design-md` | Signature purple gradients, payment UI patterns |
M|awesome-design-reference|| 8 | Raycast | `https://getdesign.md/raycast.com/design-md` | Sleek dark chrome, vibrant gradient accents, command UI |
M|awesome-design-reference|| 9 | Clay | `https://getdesign.md/clay.com/design-md` | CRM dashboard, data visualization patterns |
M|awesome-design-reference|| 10 | Coinbase | `https://getdesign.md/coinbase.com/design-md` | Fintech trust patterns — matches Hourbour |
M|awesome-design-reference|| 11 | ElevenLabs | `https://getdesign.md/elevenlabs.io/design-md` | AI product design, dark interface, audio visualization |
M|awesome-design-reference|| 12 | Figma | `https://getdesign.md/figma.com/design-md` | Design tool UI patterns, multi-panel workspace |
