M|awesome-design-reference|When designing any UI component, screen, or flow:
M|awesome-design-reference|1. Fetch the DESIGN.md of the most relevant system above using WebFetch
M|awesome-design-reference|2. Apply the component patterns, spacing, elevation, and color guidance
M|awesome-design-reference|3. Adapt to YVON's dark navy `#1A1A2E` + accent red `#E94560` palette
M|awesome-design-reference|4. Never invent design patterns from scratch — reference prd-grade systems